  "title": "COMPANY DIRECTOR",
  "description": "<p><p><strong>Strategic Leadership</strong></p><ul><li><p>Set the company’s vision, mission, and long-term strategy</p></li><li><p>Provide overall leadership and direction to the management team</p></li></ul></p><p><p><strong>Corporate Governance & Compliance</strong></p><ul><li><p>Ensure the company complies with Singapore laws, regulations, and ACRA requirements</p></li><li><p>Act in accordance with the Companies Act and fiduciary duties</p></li></ul></p><p><p><strong>Financial Oversight</strong></p><ul><li><p>Approve budgets, financial plans, and major expenditures</p></li><li><p>Monitor company financial performance and profitability</p></li><li><p>Ensure proper accounting records and internal controls are maintained</p></li></ul></p><p><p><strong>Decision-Making Authority</strong></p><ul><li><p>Make key business decisions on investments, contracts, and expansion</p></li><li><p>Approve major policies, agreements, and business transactions</p></li></ul></p><p><p><strong>Management Supervision</strong></p><ul><li><p>Appoint, guide, and evaluate senior management</p></li><li><p>Ensure effective organizational structure and operational efficiency</p></li></ul></p><p><p><strong>Risk Management</strong></p><ul><li><p>Identify business risks and implement mitigation strategies</p></li><li><p>Ensure adequate insurance and risk control measures are in place</p></li></ul></p><p><p><strong>Stakeholder & Business Relations</strong></p><ul><li><p>Represent the company to shareholders, banks, auditors, and regulators</p></li><li><p>Build and maintain relationships with key clients, partners, and vendors</p></li></ul></p><p><p><strong>Business Development</strong></p><ul><li><p>Drive company growth through new business opportunities</p></li><li><p>Oversee marketing, sales strategy, and market expansion</p></li></ul></p><p><p><strong>Human Resources Oversight</strong></p><ul><li><p>Approve key hiring decisions and remuneration policies</p></li><li><p>Ensure fair employment practices and workplace compliance</p></li></ul></p><p><p><strong>Reporting & Accountability</strong></p><ul><li><p>Report company performance to shareholders</p></li><li><p>Ensure transparency, ethical conduct, and good corporate practices</p></li></ul></p>",
